- Portret?

102
00:15:48,230 --> 00:15:52,822
Portret mog sina.
Nisti ga bacilo?

103
00:15:53,022 --> 00:15:58,135
Ne. Naravno da nisam.
- Dobro.

104
00:16:01,623 --> 00:16:03,621
Tu si.

105
00:16:07,178 --> 00:16:09,791
Na isto mesto gde ste ga ostavili.

106
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:18,819
Koliko imaš godina?
Osamnaest?

107
00:16:19,019 --> 00:16:21,936
Da.
On je bio tvojih godina.

108
00:16:22,136 --> 00:16:24,691
Kada je umro.

109
00:16:25,830 --> 00:16:28,448
Ovo je njegova soba.

110
00:16:32,791 --> 00:16:34,789
Hvala.

111
00:16:38,282 --> 00:16:40,280
Doviđenja.

112
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:57,804
