Nije potrebno.
Hvala ali ne hvala.

163
00:22:32,979 --> 00:22:34,977
Čekaj!

164
00:22:42,377 --> 00:22:44,375
Hvala.

165
00:23:10,522 --> 00:23:12,170
Ozbiljno?

166
00:23:13,589 --> 00:23:15,237
Mama?

167
00:23:18,650 --> 00:23:20,298
Tata?

168
00:23:22,828 --> 00:23:25,063
Ima li koga?

169
00:25:52,905 --> 00:25:54,903
Anita.

170
00:25:58,827 --> 00:26:00,825
Anita?

171
00:26:15,579 --> 00:26:20,860
<i>Ne, tata! Napolje!
- Gde si sinoć bila? - Nigde!</i>

172
00:26:21,059 --> 00:26:23,342
<i>Izlazi iz moje sobe!</i>

173
00:28:17,503 --> 00:28:19,501
