176
00:28:32,401 --> 00:28:36,741
Ne.
- Hoćeš da odem?

177
00:28:41,887 --> 00:28:43,885
U redu je.

178
00:29:07,277 --> 00:29:09,275
Šta mogu da uradim?

179
00:29:13,791 --> 00:29:15,789
Zaštiti me.

180
00:29:19,362 --> 00:29:21,360
U redu.

181
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:24,398
Obećavaš?

182
00:29:27,243 --> 00:29:29,324
Obećavam.

183
00:30:30,794 --> 00:30:34,776
Imate savršeno zdravu bebu.
Sve je idealno.

184
